data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. HUGE PRICE REDUCTION!! Here's your chance to live in a resort style community right in Clermont! This St Andrew model has its own Solar Heated pool! It features 2 bedrooms and 2 baths with a den. As you enter there is a large Livingroom/Dining room area and another Family room right off the Kitchen. The kitchen has granite countertops, an island for extra prep space, lots of storage including a large pantry! The kitchen and Master Bedroom open to a lovely Florida room which leads you out to your own solar heated pool! There's even an outside shower poolside. A new Trane A/C .was installed this year! There are beautiful motorized blinds in the Livingroom, Master Bedroom and on both sliding doors. And another motorized screen on the garage door! Don't worry about painting the exterior of your home as the HOA does it for you!! Kings Ride is a 55+ Community that features a multi million dollar clubhouse, 3 heated pools, Golf course, Tennis courts, bocce ball, shuffleboard, basketball and pickle ball courts, fitness center, billiards, ballroom, craft room, with clubs galore! The community has 24 hour guard gated access! Maintenance fees include lawn maintenance including trimming shrubs, irrigation systems throughout the community, cable TV, internet and home phone, and access to all its amenities. You can even drive your golf cart to the Publix shopping center next door. Come and see this beautiful pool home today!
